{
  "arquivo": "ca02_23",
  "total": 51,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "*sigh*",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Hey, Itsuki.\\nUesugi-san seems off, don't you think?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Yes, I've been worried about it too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Could it be because of our advice...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "It's like he's pushing too hard isn't it?\\nHe even invited Nino-san to shop earlier.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Maybe he made a mistake while shopping\\nand that's why he's feeling down.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Nino seemed a bit off at that time too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "I wonder if big bro and Nino are okay.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "(Futaro is acting strange.\\n He's been sighing since then.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "(Futaro wouldn't be the type to keep dwelling\\n on something like failing at making a shisa...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "(I wonder if I made a mistake when I suggested \\n making a shisa?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "(Shisa protect one's house in pairs\\n That's why I wanted to make them with Futaro.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "(I thought that if we put our creations\\n side by side, they would also protect us.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "(He looks so gloomy...\\n I might be seeing this side of Futaro\\n for the first time.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "(I'm wondering what happened?\\n He was being so proactive earlier,\\n and seemed to be having fun shopping.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "(Ugh, I can't figure this out on my own!\\n This isn't how I do things!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What is it?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Is there something on your mind?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No, nothing really%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Don't lie to me.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "You're clearly not yourself.\\nIt's as if your head is in the clouds.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Tell me. What happened?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It's really nothing.\\nI'm sorry for worrying you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Fine.\\nIf that's the case, I have an idea as well.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Everyone, I need to talk to you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "What? What's wrong, all of a sudden?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I need to talk to Futaro, alone, from now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "AH?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "We're gonna split up and do our own thing\\nfor the time being. That's fine, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hey, Nino?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Futaro, hush.\\nThis is necessary for us right now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "(Yes, if we don't talk about this now,\\n we might just grow apart.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "(I don't want that. I DON'T!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I'm fine with that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Miku?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I mean, Futaro, you've been acting strange\\nsince earlier. If Nino says she needs to talk to you,\\nthen it must be true.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "I agree with Miku.\\nLet's leave this to Nino%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "At this point, it's something that ONLY Nino can handle.\\nI don't mind either.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Me neither.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Me too!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Please take care of my big bro, Nino-san.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Thanks, everyone.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "(Now, all that's left is to talk to Futaro.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "(I'm definitely going to make you talk.\\n Prepare yourself, Futaro!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}